      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Just to point out, this is not collections specific. You get the error because Java compiler can&#39;t ensure type safety in general. For example, same warning is produced with the following code: AbstractMap.SimpleEntry&lt;String, String&gt; entry = new AbstractMap.SimpleEntry(&quot;hello&quot;, &quot;world&quot;);"
