    "question_id" : 197986,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Android Studio, you need to add:</p>\n\n<pre><code>allprojects {\n\n    gradle.projectsEvaluated {\n        tasks.withType(JavaCompile) {\n            options.compilerArgs &lt;&lt; \"-Xlint:unchecked\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    // ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>in your project's build.gradle file to know where this error is produced.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 10787503,
      "reputation" : 101,
      "user_id" : 7936081,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-u5TKiGfLWmU/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAH9E/BLcjc8sg9PU/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "Mayukh Datta",
